      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been meticulously cared for, kept tucked away in the garage, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for your next big road trip, this is definitely the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
