    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of the S54-powered era, presenting in concours-level condition. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features synchronized individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced double VANOS system, ensuring optimal cam phasing and throttle response. Power is channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid with all factory suspension kinematics preserved. This is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance and a flawless mechanical profile.",
      "price": 48500.0,
