    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero swirl marks or stone chips, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from the day it left the factory; the premium leather retains its original matte texture and factory scent, with absolutely no creasing on the seat bolsters or wear on the steering wheel. Every electronic component, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach\u2014the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the transmission shifts with silk-like precision. Included with the sale is a comprehensive binder containing every service receipt, documenting a history of preventative care that exceeds all manufacturer recommendations. With no accidents, no smoke history, and no imperfections, this is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
